    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-05-28T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-05-28T13:00:00-05:00" n="440"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d440">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.115/290: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lockhart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-05-28T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 28, 1938—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>351. Your 719, May 25, 3 p.m. The Department finds your telegram under reference
                    very helpful.</p>
                <p>Before reaching a decision in regard to the question of bringing to the attention
                    of the Japanese Government the subject of interference with American trade in
                    China, the Department would appreciate receiving additional data in regard to
                    items such as the names of the American firm referred to by you and of other
                    American firms, if any, whose business is being subjected to interference, the
                    articles of American export and import trade affected, some instances of
                    stopping Chinese craft from bringing American-owned goods to Shanghai, and any
                    other ascertainable facts.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
